The paper discusses the use of deep learning models and convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for prediction in various disciplines, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on CNNs suggests computer vision (cs.CV) as another likely sub-category.
